      out.write("            <p>â¢ The application will start at a login screen and then move into a single page that will make all the functionality and information accessible. This page will have a multi window layout to display both the active chatrooms and project calendar. This page will also include several sidebars for selecting and editing either projects, chatrooms, messages, or calendars. </p>\r\n");
